! Ayu Theme for CodeMirror 6

Simple theme with bright colors based on [[Ayu|https://github.com/ayu-theme/ayu-colors]].

!! Variants

* `ayu` / `ayu-dark` - Dark (default)
* `ayu-mirage` - Medium dark with blue tint
* `ayu-light` - Light

!! Available Theme Classes

| !Class | !Description |
| `cm6-theme-ayu` | Dark (default) |
| `cm6-theme-ayu-dark` | Same as above |
| `cm6-theme-ayu-mirage` | Mirage |
| `cm6-theme-ayu-light` | Light |
